ton College, 1869\u20131959 : an informal history |last1=Megson |first1=Barbara |last2=Lindsay |first2=Jean |author-link= |year=1961 |publisher=(no publisher) |location=Cambridge, England |isbn= |page= |pages= |url= |accessdate= |ASIN = B0000CKXTS }}\n*{{cite book |title=Emily Davies and Girton College |last=Stephen |first=Barbara Nightingale |author-link=Barbara, Lady Stephen |year=1927 |publisher=Constable |location=London, England |isbn= |page= |pages= |url= |access-date=}}\n*{{cite book |title=Girton college, 1869\u20131932 |last=Stephen |first=Barbara Nightingale |author-link = Barbara, Lady Stephen |year=1933 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |location=Cambridge, England |isbn= |pages= |url= |accessdate=}}\n*{{cite book |title=A Victorian Monument: Buildings of Girton College |last=Waterhouse |first= Prudence |author-link= |year=1990 |publisher=Prudence Waterhouse |location=Cambridge, England |isbn=978-0-9515650-0-1 |page= |pages= |url= |access-date=}}\n*{{cite book |title=Later Victorian Cambridge |last=Winstanley |first= Denys Arthur |author-link= |year=1977 |publisher = [[Arno Press]] |location=New York, NY |isbn=978-0-405-10000-0 |page= |pages= |url= |access-date=}}\n{{refend}}\n\n; Web primary sources\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite web |url = http://www.girton.cam.ac.uk/media/files/CollegeStatutes2009.pdf |title = Girton College Statutes 2009, with supplemental charter |author = Girton College |year=2009 |website= |publisher=Cambridge University Press |access-date=30 August 2011 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927015855/http://www.girton.cam.ac.uk/media/files/CollegeStatutes2009.pdf |archive-date=27 September 2011 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}\n{{refend}}\n\n; Other\n{{refbegin}}\n*{{cite web |url = http://www-groups.dcs.st-and.ac.uk/~history/Davis/Indexes/Cambridge.html |title = Davis archive of female mathematicians |first1 = A. |last1=Davis |first2=John |last2 = O'Connor |first3=Edmund |last3=Robertson |date=May 2004 |website= |access-da